    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"690858\">Daniel Weber</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/113489-new-members/topic/changing.20gt.20to.20gte.20for.20integers/near/469369230\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Maybe there's <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=Nat.add_one_le_of_lt#doc\">docs#Nat.add_one_le_of_lt</a> ?</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><code>unknown tactic</code>?</p>\n<p>I think MacBeth's course environment might be lean3? such a shame as this looks ideal.</p>",
