    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"724904\">rzeta0</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/113489-new-members/topic/changing.20gt.20to.20gte.20for.20integers/near/469372826\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><code>unknown tactic</code>?</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>You must have forgotten to write down the <code>exact</code> or <code>apply</code> tactic</p>",
