        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"724904\">rzeta0</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/113489-new-members/topic/changing.20gt.20to.20gte.20for.20integers/near/469372826\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>I think MacBeth's course environment might be lean3? such a shame as this looks ideal.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Hi, I hope I'm not intruding, and as a side note, \"The Mechanics of Proof\" does use Lean4, however there are some tactics that are programmatically excluded to ensure people learn how to use the less powerful ones.</p>",
